Install the Correct NVIDIA Legacy Driver

For GTX 750 Ti, install the 580xx legacy packages:

Command:
    sudo dnf install -y akmod-nvidia-580xx xorg-x11-drv-nvidia-580xx xorg-x11-drv-nvidia-580xx-libs xorg-x11-drv-nvidia-580xx-cuda

These packages are the correct legacy branch for Maxwell-era cards like GTX 750 Ti.
